Dropbox File Request
[Dropbox] [File Request].
	Receive large files from people who do not have Dropbox accounts
	[https://gyazo.com/c9a53d21db0a787d84529aa5cfac9fbe]
	When we create a "file request", a dedicated page is created.
	The other party can upload files from that page without an account.
	Uploaded files go into Dropbox here.

	A user who opens the URL looks like this
		[https://gyazo.com/eea1ab310dcc17008af842867299860d]
	When the file is uploaded I get an email notification and on the screen it looks like this
		[https://gyazo.com/dce162ce847826a50f30203b7f0e9ca8]

	I haven't checked, but maybe, unlike sharing a folder, if you collect files from multiple people, each submitter can't see what the other submitter has submitted.
		In other words, useful for use cases such as accepting report submissions